  "title": "Recruitment Consultant",
  "description": "<p>Job Summary:<br>\nResponsible for end-to-end spectrum of hiring activities and updating candidates on the interview outcome and recruitment process.<br>\nWork with clients to define necessary requirements for open roles.<br>\nSource for active and passive candidates.<br>\nPlace qualified candidates in a timely manner and ensure that pre-onboarding processes are completed promptly.<br>\n<br>\nRequirements:<br>\nThose without relevant experience are welcome to apply.<br>\nExperience in headhunting, client acquisition, business development will be an advantage.<br>\nSuccessful candidates are required to attain a Certificate of Employment Intermediaries (CEI)<br>\n<br>\nGood communication, interpersonal and persuasion abilities.<br>\nAble to handle sensitive matters with tact and discretion.<br>\nGood attention to detail, sense of urgency and follow-up skills.<br>\nGood time-management skills with the ability to handle multiple roles independently.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Lawrence Chua</p>\n<p>Han Sing Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>MOM EA 23C1646</p>\n<p>EA Reg No: R1220679</p>\n<p>Interested Pls WhatsApp: +65 94559590</p>",
